title: Does Free Will Exist?
description:
My response to the popular claims that Free Will doesn't exist. If the atheists are right about God, then they are right here.

This is episode 24 of my podcast.  

Make sure to like and subscribe!

Check out my podcast: Fining Ideas | The Colton Kirby Show: https://anchor.fm/coltonkirby
